---
import articleimg from "../images/blog/illustration-article.svg";
import avatar from "../images/blog/image-avatar.webp";
---

<style>
  @import url("https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Figtree:wght@600&display=swap");
  @import url("https://unpkg.com/css.gg@2.0.0/icons/css/home-alt.css");

  * {
    box-sizing: border-box;
    font-family: "Figtree", sans-serif;
    margin: 0px;
    padding: 0;
  }

  body {
    background-color: hsl(47, 88%, 63%);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    min-height: 100vh;
    margin: auto;
    font-size: 16px;
  }
  .card {
    display: grid;
    max-width: 380px;
    height: 525px;
    padding: 1.25rem;

    border: 1px solid black;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    background-color: hsl(0, 0%, 100%);
    box-shadow: 10px 10px 0px 0px rgba(0, 0, 0, 1);
  }

  .card img {
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
  }

  .card h1 {
    padding-top: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }
  .card h1:hover {
    color: hsl(47, 88%, 63%);
  }

  .card p:nth-child(2) {
    font-weight: 100;
  }

  .card__chip {
    background-color: hsl(47, 88%, 63%);
    padding: 0.5em 1rem;
    margin: 1rem 0;
    font-weight: bold;
    border-radius: 0.25rem;
    border: none;
    width: max-content;
  }
  .card__chip:hover {
    cursor: pointer;
    background-color: hsl(0, 0%, 7%);
    color: hsl(0, 0%, 100%);
  }

  .content {
    color: hsl(0, 0%, 50%);
    line-height: 1.5;
    padding: 0.5rem 0rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .user {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .user img {
    width: 10%;
  }

  a {
    align-self: flex-start;
    left: 3rem;
    top: 3rem;
    position: absolute;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    color: hsl(0, 0%, 100%);
  }

  a:link {
    color: hsl(0, 0%, 100%);
  }

  svg {
    line-height: 1;
    height: 1em;
    width: 1em;
  }
</style>

<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<main>
  <a href="/">
    <svg
      width="24"
      height="24"
      viewBox="0 0 24 24"
      fill="none"
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    >
      <path
        fill-rule="evenodd"
        clip-rule="evenodd"
        d="M6 22.8787C4.34315 22.8787 3 21.5355 3 19.8787V9.87866C3 9.84477 3.00169 9.81126 3.00498 9.77823H3C3 9.20227 3.2288 8.64989 3.63607 8.24262L9.87868 2.00002C11.0502 0.828445 12.9497 0.828445 14.1213 2.00002L20.3639 8.24264C20.7712 8.6499 21 9.20227 21 9.77823H20.995C20.9983 9.81126 21 9.84477 21 9.87866V19.8787C21 21.5355 19.6569 22.8787 18 22.8787H6ZM12.7071 3.41423L19 9.70713V19.8787C19 20.4309 18.5523 20.8787 18 20.8787H15V15.8787C15 14.2218 13.6569 12.8787 12 12.8787C10.3431 12.8787 9 14.2218 9 15.8787V20.8787H6C5.44772 20.8787 5 20.4309 5 19.8787V9.7072L11.2929 3.41423C11.6834 3.02371 12.3166 3.02371 12.7071 3.41423Z"
        fill="hsl(0, 0%, 100%)"></path>
    </svg>
    Home
  </a>
  <div class="card">
    <img src={articleimg.src} alt="card image" />
    <section>
      <p class="card__chip">Learning</p>
      <p>Published 21 Dec 2023</p>
      <h1>HTML & CSS foundations</h1>
      <p class="content">
        These languages are the backbone of every website, defining structure,
        content, and presentation.
      </p>

      <div class="user">
        <img src={avatar.src} alt="user-profile" />
        <h4>Greg Hooper</h4>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</main>
